{"tid":2233260,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府飛行服務隊不評論是否曾偵察追蹤12名港人涉偷渡","createTime":"2020-10-07T04:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T00:24:59.000Z","uid":291865,"like":5,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"2d2bf38ce36ba94800cecb01fcb4f129f2f44305","tid":2233260,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:00:00.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政府飛行服務隊不評論12名港人涉嫌偷渡被內地當局截獲當日，是否曾派飛機或直升機進行偵察及追蹤。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果日報》 日前報道指，今年8月23日，12名港人涉嫌偷渡當日清晨，政府飛行服務隊定翼機曾出動，在他們登上快艇前，在布袋澳上空盤旋，及後在快艇航線上空盤旋飛行，疑似空中偵察及追蹤目標，質疑本港有份通知內地追截。而在快艇被截獲後，亦有飛行服務隊的直升機飛往涉事地點。<br />\n<br />\n政府飛行服務隊回覆查詢說，按一貫做法不會公開飛行任務的細節，不評論有關報道。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=408122&amp;home=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D408122%26home%3D1&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmYVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=b797f141\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D408122%26home%3D1&h=20f0708f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=408122&amp;home=1</a>"},{"pid":"b6cc9a411fe74c8f49f4634f91077b60cd322711","tid":2233260,"uid":47674,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:04:53.000Z","msg":"不如用番個舊名輔助空軍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99941c3c077637bac8c23d7708ca89c08b534540","tid":2233260,"uid":126366,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:07:42.000Z","msg":"根本就on撚9<br />\n乜撚嘢不評論<br />\n咁咪即係認撚咗"},{"pid":"fd9a599e498e4bd66733087b4c79d506f74a48ee","tid":2233260,"uid":18894,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:08:42.000Z","msg":"不會公開飛行任務的<span class=\"red\">細節</span><br />\n但連大約係咩任務都無講 搜索?救援? 唔敢講"},{"pid":"5561164151ff7aa0b3f1730849a597a6bbdec716","tid":2233260,"uid":76674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:08:57.000Z","msg"